Package: fcoint
Type: Package
Title: Fourier Cointegration Tests for Time Series with Smooth Structural Breaks
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: person("Muhammad", "Alkhalaf", email = "muhammedalkhalaf@gmail.com",
    role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
    comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0002-2677-9246"))
Description: Implements four Fourier-based cointegration tests that allow for
    smooth structural breaks via trigonometric terms: the Fourier ADL test
    (FADL) of Banerjee, Arcabic and Lee (2017)
    <doi:10.1016/j.econmod.2017.03.004>, the Fourier Engle-Granger tests
    (FEG and FEG2), and the Tsong, Lee, Tsai and Hu (2016)
    <doi:10.1007/s00181-015-0921-5> test. Lag and frequency selection is
    performed via AIC or BIC. Critical values are included for 1, 5, and 10
    percent significance levels.
Author: Muhammad Alkhalaf [aut, cre, cph]
    (<https://orcid.org/0009-0002-2677-9246>)
Maintainer: Muhammad Alkhalaf <muhammedalkhalaf@gmail.com>
